Package controller.gameController

Class NormalGameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.gameController.GameController
      • controller.gameController.NormalGameController
  • public class NormalGameController
extends GameController

    NormalGameController

    This class extends from GameController and initialises the information demonstration and load the map for Hard game mode. It enable the change of Ends status. It applied MapReader to read in a game map in txt type and load game elements to the scene in order to im[rove the extendability.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.4
    Author:
    Kejia Wu, scykw1@nottingham.ac.uk
    See Also:
    GameController, MapReader
